The top and bottom halves can be mixed and matched with other Swap Force characters to create customized characters that come to life in the game. A speedy torso wielding a sword can be swapped for a heavily armoured, bomb-touting upper half. If all the Swap Force are purchased, there are 256 possible combinations.
